metadata.description:
Endless Color is a song from the 80s, from the future. 

Produced by Matti Free & Glassface, Endless Color is just a dang good time. Bouncy drums, rocking guitar and synths, heartwarming vocals. Let's have fun yall. This will be the first of a string of several releases to kick off 2023.
